@page "/"

<PageTitle>Conductor Sizing - Dimensionamento de Condutores Elétricos</PageTitle>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center py-12 px-4">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                Motor de Cálculo NBR 5410:2004
            </div>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
                Dimensionamento de
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text gradient-primary inline-block">
                    Condutores Elétricos
                </span>
            </h1>

            <!-- Subtitle -->
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Sistema inteligente para dimensionamento técnico de condutores de baixa tensão
                com cálculos automáticos e relatórios profissionais.
            </p>

            <!-- CTA Buttons -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
                <a href="/dimensionamento" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white gradient-primary rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                    </svg>
                    Iniciar Dimensionamento
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Features Grid -->
<div class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Cálculos Conforme Norma NBR 5410:2004
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Todos os critérios técnicos aplicados automaticamente para garantir instalações seguras
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Corrente de Projeto</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Cálculo preciso baseado em potência, tensão, fator de potência e rendimento do equipamento.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Fatores de Correção</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Aplicação automática de FCT, FCA e FRT conforme temperatura, agrupamento e tipo de solo.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Capacidade de Condução</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Seleção automática da bitola através das Tabelas 36 (PVC) e 37 (XLPE/EPR) da norma.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Queda de Tensão</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Verificação automática do limite de 4% estabelecido pela norma para circuitos terminais.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Condutor de Proteção</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dimensionamento automático do PE conforme Tabela 58, garantindo proteção adequada.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 6 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md card-hover border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Histórico em Memória</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Gerenciamento thread-safe de dimensionamentos com histórico completo em tempo real.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Info Banner -->
<div class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
                <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0 md:pr-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Pronto para começar?</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-100">
                        Dimensione seus condutores em segundos com precisão técnica e conformidade normativa.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a href="/dimensionamento" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-purple-600 font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap">
                    Calcular Agora
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Technical Info -->
<div class="py-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="px-8">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Sobre o Sistema</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Motor de cálculo profissional desenvolvido para engenheiros eletricistas, projetistas e estudantes. 
                Implementa fielmente todos os critérios da <strong>ABNT NBR 5410:2004</strong> para dimensionamento 
                de condutores elétricos em instalações de baixa tensão.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
                    .NET 8
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
                    Blazor Server
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
                    Tempo Real
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
                    Thread-Safe
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
                    Containerizado
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
